t can still be observed and controlled in spite of these failures\". The paper proposes a model of failures a little bit more complex than the usual \'belongs or not to the giant component\', the interactions are presented as a list of four points. The results of the simulations performed in this study sugest that a higher ICC lead to a higer robustness.','proceedings'),('Modelling interdependencies between the electricity and information infrastructures','Springer','not-in-selection',2007,'','','proceedings'),('Modelling interdependent infrastructures using interacting dynamical models','Inderscience','not-in-selection',2008,'','','journal'),('Modularity and community structure in networks','NAS','not-in-selection',2006,'','','journal'),('Modularity and extreme edges of the Internet','APS','not-in-selection',2003,'','','journal'),('Multi-layer capacity planning for IP-optical networks','IEEE','not-in-selection',2014,'','','journal'),('Multi-layer restoration in hierarchical IP/MPLS over WSON networks','IEEE','not-in-selection',2012,'','','proceedings'),('Multi-level learning based memetic algorithm for community detection','ScienceDirect','not-in-selection',2014,'','','journal'),('Multilayer networks','Oxford','not-in-selection',2014,'','','journal'),('Multiple routing configurations for fast IP network recovery','IEEE','not-in-selection',2009,'','','journal'),('Multiplexity-facilitated cascades in networks','APS','not-in-selection',2012,'','','journal'),('Multirelational organization of large-scale social networks in an online world','NAS','not-in-selection',2010,'','','journal'),('MuxViz: a tool for multilayer analysis and visualization of networks','Oxford Un.','not-in-selection',2014,'','','journal'),('Navigability of interconnected networks under random failures','NAS','not-in-selection',2014,'','','journal'),('Network analysis: methodological foundations','Springer','not-in-selection',2005,'','','book'),('Network Centrality, Measures of','ScienceDirect','not-